{"tid":1537344,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[求變] 我地係唔可以犯法 要做一個良好既公民!","createTime":"2019-09-04T01:45:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-04T01:56:24.000Z","uid":298823,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"b249e926eb8eb3e64333cf5ecbacb98f9cb7b5d3","tid":1537344,"uid":298823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T01:45:05.000Z","msg":"身為香港人當然唔可以犯法 特別係非法集結<br />\n呢D破壞社會安寧既行動 所以我成日都發惡夢<br />\n每一次惡夢都係成班黑衫人聚集係同一個地方大叫口號<br />\n而呢個做法就係非常好既理據俾狗以 非法集結 咬人<br />\n而非法集結最緊要既成份係 集結 二字<br />\n簡單黎講 集結係要一班人停係到先可以構成集結<br />\n大家有無發現到當我地成班人出去行個時<br />\n係無狗咬人<br />\n原因當然可能係咁多人既行動 佢地咬唔哂<br />\n但其實最大既原因係我地無集結到 我地無停留係同一個地方<br />\n咁為左做守法既公民 我地係咪唔應該停留係同一個地方太耐<br />\n仲要著哂黑衫荒死人唔知我地係有關係<br />\n為左求變 可以以集會變成流水式表達訴求<br />\n但係怕因為有人唔熟香港既路會有危險<br />\n所以我地應該要指定一個區域 而黑色物件作精神標記 <br />\n方便行得耐天氣熱而更換 但唔可以再著黑衫 因為衫著得耐會好易臭<br />\n沿途可以經過好多緊要既地點 但唔需要停留都可以<br />\n去表達我地夢想既野 因為當我表達完<br />\n我就會行去前面表達 後面既人就會代替我再表達 <br />\n咁係個同一點地點既人聽到都係不斷既夢想叫喊<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06707bfb883105cd40b9d2c390d1f937b5509452","tid":1537344,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T01:45:45.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月7日 (六) 1PM<br />\n機場交通壓力測試 (重考)</strong></div><br />\n<br />\n香港市民：<br />\n✅ 以遊客身份入機場觀賞飛機升降 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 唔識路就坐多幾轉車 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 必需繳付車資乘坐黨鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n烏克蘭, 法國等其他國藉居民：<br />\n各有各做, 自由發揮, 唔割但要小心 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n另外可參考唔揸春袋揸輸精管方法: <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n [行動post] 肯入黎睇9.7點樣揸機場輸精管未 | LIHKG <br />\n <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1</a> <br />\n <br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nyixFQQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnyixFQQ.png&h=cc1f24a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月8日 (日) 2PM<br />\n香港人權與民主法案集會<br />\n美國駐港澳總領事館</strong></div><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2GKH20p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2GKH20p.png&h=6178433f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"16553576dd3d90d803690968b745720cd9fbfe77","tid":1537344,"uid":134107,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T01:46:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mqNCcpj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmqNCcpj.jpg&h=145b357e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n[10月1送大禮]「和理拍」一齊推上聯合國人權理事會！！!<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1536307\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1536307</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"6b66bc557149d806a51efde95c32f76044364a6d","tid":1537344,"uid":304228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T01:55:17.000Z","msg":"打咁多字好似都辭不達意咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b143a780278169a47b542d7706ba194226c03fe","tid":1537344,"uid":267425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T01:56:24.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>解散警隊 刻不容緩</strong></span></span><br />\n我屌曬你地老母快啲推第六大訴求<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1536852\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1536852</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fLDFcUN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfLDFcUN.jpg&h=350c6ca1&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}